query: SELECT DISTINCT e.turmaId, t.codigo, COUNT(e.id) as total_eventos FROM eventos e JOIN turmas t ON e.turmaId = t.id WHERE e.dataEvento IS NOT NULL GROUP BY e.turmaId, t.codigo ORDER BY total_eventos DESC LIMIT 5
